{"title":"红与蓝","date":"2019-03-17T15:32:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 17, 2019","L":"03/17/2019","MM-DD":"03-17"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/BaXoeALfGZP8q4j.jpg","link":"2019/03/17/红与蓝","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.499Z","content":"<blockquote><p>微风徐徐<br>\n田间金黄色的麦子<br>\n一簇簇擦着肩<br>\n涔涔的麦香把我留住</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>提着编织袋<br>\n沿着门前那条土路<br>\n悠闲地走着</p>\n<p>袋子上印满了格子<br>\n蓝色的和红色的<br>\n沉默着像是在说话</p>\n<p>微风徐徐<br>\n田间金黄色的麦子<br>\n一簇簇擦着肩<br>\n涔涔的麦香把我留住</p>\n<p>一辆拖拉机叫嚣着过去了<br>\n我连忙退开<br>\n车上载满了一袋又一带的<br>\n红色和蓝色的格子</p>\n","prev":{"title":"蜃","link":"2019/10/26/蜃"},"next":{"title":"枫","link":"2018/11/15/枫"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2019/03/17/红与蓝/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦 Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"130 words in 1 min"}